{"tid":2157244,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"袁彌昌:特朗普選情靠林鄭？","createTime":"2020-08-15T02:12:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T02:41:24.000Z","uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"469ddac3cac639789d8ebaa4feceb886c6102d4f","tid":2157244,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T02:12:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/column/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%e7%89%b9%e6%9c%97%e6%99%ae%e9%81%b8%e6%83%85%e9%9d%a0%e6%9e%97%e9%84%ad%ef%bc%9f-230637?fbclid=IwAR1I1UbODy_ppp1qmkDynxctaXhBBmNuSbQz0gQHX6mzED-_J4ihgrUwmt4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fcolumn%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25e7%2589%25b9%25e6%259c%2597%25e6%2599%25ae%25e9%2581%25b8%25e6%2583%2585%25e9%259d%25a0%25e6%259e%2597%25e9%2584%25ad%25ef%25bc%259f-230637%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1I1UbODy_ppp1qmkDynxctaXhBBmNuSbQz0gQHX6mzED-_J4ihgrUwmt4&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8S9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=f6473196\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/column/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%e7%89%b9%e6%9c%97%e6%99%ae%e9%81%b8%e6%83%85%e9%9d%a0%e6%9e%97%e9%84%ad%ef%bc%9f-230637?fbclid=IwAR1I1UbODy_ppp1qmkDynxctaXhBBmNuSbQz0gQHX6mzED-_J4ihgrUwmt4</a><br />\n<br />\n美國總統大選將於11月3日舉行，特朗普本來希望藉疫情和郵寄投票不公來推遲選舉，可惜如意算盤打不響，只好改打林鄭月娥主意，以美國財政部名義，制裁以林鄭月娥為首的11名中港官員─堂堂美國總統，居然要乞靈於林鄭，證明特朗普也被迫得急了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現在距離大選不夠3個月，中美關係瀕臨破裂，美國又缺乏制勝板斧，實際上特朗普已不可能指望靠與中國達成協議或在角力中佔得上風，來爭取國民支持。所以如今之計，就只有想辦法將行動直接轉化為選票，以挽救選情，因此消費香港問題變得事在必行。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">事實上，上周正當港交所氣勢如虹，股價屢創新高之際，特朗普卻表示香港失去了特殊待遇後，將不再是一個成功的交易所，美國交易所將因此賺更多錢。此舉顯示特朗普已到了一個技窮的地步，不惜出口術和消費香港，以作為連任的最後的強心針。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">特朗普政府除了期望制裁中港官員此舉能直接轉化為選票之外，還有給予香港民主派道義上的支持，以及激起北京的強烈反應這兩種用意。這個道義上的支持不僅遲來了許久，充其量亦只是道義上而已，對改變北京的行為毫無幫助，甚至只會令香港形勢更形惡化。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於激起北京的強烈反應這一點，換作平常情況可能會奏效，但北京現在眼見特朗普的選情大幅落後於拜登，只消觀望到11月大選便知分曉，<span class=\"red\">除基本反制以外，根本毋須來真。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">即使大選仍有變數，但這樣下去很可能特朗普博連任不成，反令林鄭變成板蕩忠臣而得以成功連任，這將會是對港人特別是民主派的最大諷刺。</span>"},{"pid":"1c45deab601570f40e2723cb495fd52fa614ac27","tid":2157244,"uid":35920,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T02:15:26.000Z","msg":"你老豆幫你鋪好晒條路<br />\n你就走去做戇鳩藍屍<br />\n真係人蠢冇藥醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49ca1e7dc98429933d17634fa534c07b3d1c3d30","tid":2157244,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T02:16:22.000Z","msg":"袁彌昌是誰"},{"pid":"facf4af08e977a8a5ce3ceb7be523c65c70cfafc","tid":2157244,"uid":19986,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T02:18:38.000Z","msg":"想同老豆割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"152ce21bf2e79bd6964d4b4272e6c319bb778b38","tid":2157244,"uid":127575,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T02:23:38.000Z","msg":"睇錯以為係袁彌明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faa4eda4ecc69d6ced421773c19aed4416e6a00d","tid":2157244,"uid":127575,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"facf4af08e977a8a5ce3ceb7be523c65c70cfafc","tid":2157244,"uid":19986,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T02:18:38.000Z","msg":"想同老豆割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T02:24:23.000Z","msg":"我係老豆寧願生舊叉燒都好過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07d7ea96951f872fe37cb5574f342729317edd23","tid":2157244,"uid":21028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T02:25:36.000Z","msg":"林鄭？ 我諗美國人十個九個都當佢市長咁嘅級數<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 制裁個市長就有助選情？<br />\n<br />\n睇到自己咁高呀？"},{"pid":"51d19c5bd6d1b633a6030b6c5c530355a44c47f4","tid":2157244,"uid":226956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T02:38:22.000Z","msg":"佢即係話燈王買拜登贏？侵侵表示真係多謝晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ba57c728c4978e296576307bed1fa5851e4a308","tid":2157244,"uid":271807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49ca1e7dc98429933d17634fa534c07b3d1c3d30","tid":2157244,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T02:16:22.000Z","msg":"袁彌昌是誰"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T02:41:24.000Z","msg":"袁弓夷個仔，容海恩老公"}]}